    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i just read somewhere online that it only matters if you drink a huge amount of it, like a whole liter or something. if i just have like a small splash in my water or a tiny bit in a smoothie, it shouldn't actually change anything in my blood right? it's just fruit so it's probably fine for a small amount.",
